events.html: • 1882 – American Old West: Robert Ford kills Jesse James.[10]

events.html: • 1888 – Jack the Ripper: The first of 11 unsolved brutal murders of women committed in or near the impoverished Whitechapel district in the East End of London, occurs.[12]
